msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_12_01_noville/narrator12"
msgid "Friendly tank destroyers approaching, just in time!"
msgstr "Cazacarros amigos acercándose ¡Justo a tiempo!"

msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_12_01_noville/narrator13"
msgid "They've flanked us! The Germans are attacking from the southeast!"
msgstr "¡Nos han flanqueado! ¡Los alemanes atacan desde el sudeste!"

msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_12_01_noville/narrator14"
msgid "They are running away! Well done!"
msgstr "¡Están huyendo! ¡Bien hecho!"

# removed
# msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_12_01_noville/narrator_desobry04"
# msgid "Good work! Our firepower has greatly increased thanks to those repaired tanks and guns!"
# msgid "Good work! "
# msgstr ""
msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_12_01_noville/narrator_desobry05"
msgid "The minefields will help slow any incoming German armor!"
msgstr ""
"Los campos de minas ayudarán a ralentizar el avance de los blindados alemanes"

msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_12_01_noville/outro_completed"
msgid ""
" Well done! You have bought enough time for the rest of the 101st to set up "
"defenses and prepare for a German attack. You may have made the difference "
"between keeping or losing Bastogne."
msgstr ""
" ¡Bien hecho! Has ganado tiempo suficiente para que el resto de la 101 "
"establezca defensas y se prepare para un ataque alemán. Posiblemente hayas "
"sido la diferencia entre mantener o perder Bastoña."

msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_12_01_noville/outro_failed"
msgid ""
"Our comrades in Bastogne will now face the entire German force unprepared. "
"If only you could have bought them some more time! Bastogne will fall, and "
"the Germans will have an open road to the Meuse River. You must try again!"
msgstr ""
"Nuestros camaradas en Bastoña se enfrentarán a toda la fuerza alemana sin "
"poder prepararse. Si les hubieras dado algo de tiempo... Bastoña caerá y los "
"alemanes tendrán un camino directo hacia el río Mosa ¡Debes intentarlo de "
"nuevo!"

msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_12_01_noville/place"
msgid "101st Airborne Division \"Screaming Eagles\""
msgstr "101ª División Aerotransportada \"Screaming Eagles\""

msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_12_01_noville/story"
msgid ""
"  Just three days ago, a German surprise offensive smashed through the "
"allied lines in the Ardennes. Initially, they advance rapidly. They aim to "
"take Antwerp. The German 5th army has orders to cross the Meuse River at "
"Dinant and Namur, without which a push to Antwerp is simply out of the "
"question.\n"
"\n"
"  To get to those bridges, they will need to take Bastogne. The 2nd Panzer "
"Division intends to pass through Noville to outflank the Bastogne defenders "
"from the north.\n"
"\n"
" However, in Noville, a small force from the 10th armored division blocks "
"their way. The first battalion of the 506th PIR moves forward to reinforce "
"them.\n"
"\n"
" Good luck!"
msgstr ""
"  Hace sólo tres días, un ataque sorpresa alemana rompió las líneas aliadas "
"en las Ardenas. Avanzan rápido. Su objetivo es tomar Amberes. El 5º ejército "
"alemán tiene órdenes de cruzar el río Mosa en Dinant y Namur, si no lo "
"consiguen, no podrán llegar a Amberes.\n"
"\n"
"  Para llegar a esos puentes, necesitarán tomar Bastoña. La 2ª División "
"Panzer pretende pasar por Noville para flanquear desde el norte a las tropas "
"que defienden Bastoña.\n"
"\n"
" Sin embargo, en Noville, una pequeña fuerza de la 10ª División Blindada les "
"bloquea el paso. El primer batallón del 506º PIR avanza para reforzarlos.\n"
"\n"
" ¡Suerte!"

msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_12_01_noville/task01"
msgid "Clear Noville of the Germans!"
msgstr "¡Despeja Noville de alemanes!"

msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_12_01_noville/task02"
msgid "Prepare to defend Noville."
msgstr "Prepárate para defender Noville."

msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_12_01_noville/task03"
msgid "Repair the damaged vehicles."
msgstr "Repara los vehículos dañados."

msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_12_01_noville/task04"
msgid ""
"Lay mines in front of the defense line before the attack starts (at least 50 "
"mines)."
msgstr ""
"Coloca minas delante de la línea defensiva antes de que comience el ataque "
"(al menos 50 minas)."

msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_12_01_noville/task05"
msgid "Hold Noville at all cost!"
msgstr "¡Defiende Noville a toda costa!"

msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_12_01_noville/task06"
msgid "Destroy enemy rocket artillery!"
msgstr "¡Destruye la artillería de cohetes enemiga!"

msgctxt "mission/single/041-usa_airborne/1944_12_01_noville/timer"
msgid "Time left before another enemy attack:"
msgstr "Tiempo restante antes de otro ataque enemigo:"
